    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>
                <date>June 2<hi rend="sup">nd</hi> 1851</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Enclosed I send<lb/> you check on Union Bank New York for<lb/>
                Twenty Seven Dollars which please distribute<lb/> as follows viz take $3. as my
                yearly subscription<lb/> to the Occident the balance of twenty four<lb/> dollars is
                the <sic>ammount</sic> subscribed by the members<lb/> of the congregation Shearith
                Israel for the benefit<lb/> of our poor brethren in <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName>
                and as I<lb/> do not know who is authorized to receive the<lb/>
                <sic>ammount</sic> at present for the purpose of <sic>transmition</sic><lb/> I
                therefore send it to you knowing that you<lb/> will take proper steps to transmit it to<lb/>
                <placeName>London</placeName> or wherever it is necessary.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I must<lb/> inform you that the <persName>Rev Ellis Lyons</persName>
                was<lb/> yesterday unanimously <sic>Ellected</sic> minister of<lb/> our congregation
                for 2 years in place of the <persName>Rev<lb/> Mr Rosenfeld</persName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Trusting this may meet you in the<lb/> enjoyment of good health I
                subscribe myself</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">Your Friend &amp; Obt Servt</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">E. Sommers</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <hi rend="underline">paid</hi>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia Pa</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
